name: alloc::collections::btree::node::Handle::<collections::btree::node::NodeRef<collections::btree::node::marker::Mut<'a>, K, V, collections::btree::node::marker::Leaf>, collections::btree::node::marker::Edge>::insert_fit
doc:
Inserts a new key-value pair between the key-value pairs to the right and left of
 this edge. This method assumes that there is enough space in the node for the new
 pair to fit.
